New interior and exterior paint. Remodeled bathroom, with new tile, vanity, bathtub, shower and lighting. The home has 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. The home boasts nice floor-plan with approximately 740 sq. ft of living space. Interior laundry room and separate Living room. 1 Car garage. The lot for the property is zoned R-3 which may allow for 2 more units to be built. This home is located on an quiet interior street in a peaceful and desirable neighborhood. Bring your most discerning buyers

Property situated on a R3 lot with long gated driveway leading to a huge oversized garage with 2 car garage door opening. Behind the garage is a yard waiting to be turned into a private garden. This home is perfect for extended families or for use as a duplex. Front of the property has 2 bedrooms 1 bath with new laminate flooring throughout, living room steps up into a large dining area, breakfast bar and gallery kitchen. Back of the property is separated from the front by laundry room and door and has is own exterior entrance. Back of the property has laminate flooring throughout, an open living room and kitchen, full bath and one bedroom. Perfect for use as a single family home or multiple family home as it is set up now, title shows the property as 4 bedroom 2 bath, must see to appreciate the true potential of this property. Additional features included new exterior and interior paint, new laminate flooring throughout, lighting package and more.

Pride of Ownership! Huge clean house. Imagine yourself coming into this amazing Spanish style house that sits on one of the best areas in the city of Bell. This house is in great shape and it is in a ready to move in condition. The homeowners have taken excellent care of the house that will be a delight for the next lucky family. Lots of the original character has been preserved, like the tall coved ceilings as well as the amazing details on the walls on the bedrooms. Cozy up next to the fireplace while having a great time with your family in the living room. Excellent house in an Excellent neighborhood, come and see it for yourself.
